{"tid":611183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"業委挪用管理費墊支罰款 民建聯僭建要居民埋單","createTime":"2018-03-30T17:12:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T17:26:15.000Z","uid":70105,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"41bb53999203246a660a362d2969ac3727aff9ef","tid":611183,"uid":70105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:12:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180331/58016085\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180331%2F58016085&d=1rRYkwox2c35Iw131GJFop4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=22a939e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180331%2F58016085&h=cb78120b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180331/58016085</a><br />\n<br />\n...............2015年時任區議員潘進源的辦事處被揭僭建，須支付57萬元款項予地政總署，但最終竟由屋苑管理費「埋單」，引起居民不滿。<br />\n<br />\n潘進源現為民建聯中央委員和麗晶花園業委會主席，曾經多次連任麗晶選區的區議員，直至2016年才敗選。他擔任區議員期間，租用麗晶花園11座地下空地作辦事處，被揭屬於僭建兼違反土地用途，地政總署追收約57萬元豁免費。業委會竟建議先由管理費支付57萬元，責任和分攤問題容後再議，業委會最後通過決議，變相數千戶居民為潘進源僭建「埋單」。 ...........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/011047_01995305263503663f78266ab273fbde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F011047_01995305263503663f78266ab273fbde.jpg&h=83a6fd53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n潘進源（圖）議員辦事處被揭僭建，須支付57萬元款項予地政總署，但最終竟由屋苑管理費「埋單」。（設計圖片／受訪者提供圖片）(資料圖片)"},{"pid":"6b669c66df9ce4a651d1d636b6ea381a95f0a728","tid":611183,"uid":18350,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:17:43.000Z","msg":"冇問題呀<br />\n個度d人投佢做區議員<br />\n係應該承受返個後果"},{"pid":"9c6f7d69c7b8acc26dbc9683a993e3d24a8fbef9","tid":611183,"uid":36251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b669c66df9ce4a651d1d636b6ea381a95f0a728","tid":611183,"uid":18350,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:17:43.000Z","msg":"冇問題呀<br />\n個度d人投佢做區議員<br />\n係應該承受返個後果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:20:42.000Z","msg":"仲有啲7頭成日懶懶閒咁業主大會永遠唔出現<br />\n人地問佢拎授權又on99簽俾人"},{"pid":"6d67047951cd2a338a570cac3be124b5a1ce7863","tid":611183,"uid":70105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b669c66df9ce4a651d1d636b6ea381a95f0a728","tid":611183,"uid":18350,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:17:43.000Z","msg":"冇問題呀<br />\n個度d人投佢做區議員<br />\n係應該承受返個後果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T17:26:15.000Z","msg":"其實係舊聞了, 佢之後選區會即輸<br />\n但果57萬到今時今日仲未收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}